dc_title_s: Index, assessment maps, Borough of East Rutherford, Bergen County, New Jersey
dc_description_s: Map showing waterways: Hackensack River, Berry's Creek, Ackerman's Creek, and Fish Creek as they relate to the properties and roadways in the Meadowlands area of East Rutherford, New Jersey|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Year is inferred by revision notes; main year on map is 1931; however there are revisions listed up until 1964.
